April,

Thank you for the timely follow up. The violations I am seeking are those
issued under MCC 10-8-526, which governs enforcement of Chicago Transit
Authority ordinances. This includes all sub-codes in the 016-110-1.xx
series and the 98-126 series issued under 10-8-526.

If your system allows filtering by issuing unit, the relevant units are 701
(Public Transportation), 702 (CTA Security Unit), and 704 (Transit Security
Unit).

I am seeking annual totals of fines levied and fines collected for
violations in this code series, broken out by year for calendar years 2018
through present, along with any outstanding balances written off or
referred to collections.

Electronic format is preferred.

Michael Russo
michael@policytorque.com

